sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TAS as TrustyAI Service<br/>8443/TCP
    participant KServe as KServe InferenceService<br/>443/TCP mTLS
    participant DB as PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>5432/3306 TCP TLS1.2+
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS mTLS

    Note over User,Prom: Flow 1: TrustyAI Model Monitoring

    KServe->>TAS: Inference Payload<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>mTLS (Istio)
    TAS->>DB: Store Metrics/Payloads<br/>PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional)<br/>Username/Password
    TAS->>Prom: Export Metrics<br/>HTTPS/9443<br/>mTLS
    User->>Route: GET /api/v1/*<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
    Route->>Proxy: Forward Request<br/>HTTPS/8443
    Proxy->>TAS: Authorized Request<br/>After SAR Check
    TAS-->>Proxy: Monitoring Data
    Proxy-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: JSON Response

    participant UserAPI as User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Operator as TrustyAI Operator
    participant KueueAPI as Kueue API
    participant JobPod as LMEval Job Pod
    participant Driver as LMES Driver<br/>18080/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelAPI as Model Endpoint<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over UserAPI,S3: Flow 2: LMEval Job Execution

    UserAPI->>K8sAPI: Create LMEvalJob CR<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>TLS 1.3<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch Event
    Operator->>KueueAPI: Create Workload<br/>In-cluster API<br/>ServiceAccount
    KueueAPI->>JobPod: Schedule Job
    JobPod->>Driver: Coordinate Tasks<br/>HTTP/18080<br/>None (sidecar)
    JobPod->>ModelAPI: Evaluate Model<br/>HTTPS/443 or HTTP/8080<br/>TLS 1.2+ or None<br/>API Key or mTLS
    JobPod->>S3: Upload Results<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS Signature V4
    S3-->>JobPod: Confirmation
    Driver-->>JobPod: Task Complete

    participant LLMApp as LLM Application
    participant Gateway as Guardrails Gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    participant Orch as Orchestrator<br/>8032/TCP HTTP
    participant Detectors as Built-in Detectors<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant ExtDetector as External Detector<br/>443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant LLMInf as LLM InferenceService<br/>443/TCP HTTPS mTLS

    Note over LLMApp,LLMInf: Flow 3: Guardrails Orchestration

    LLMApp->>Gateway: Request<br/>HTTP/8090<br/>None
    Gateway->>Orch: Forward<br/>HTTP/8032<br/>None
    Orch->>Detectors: Check Built-in<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>None
    Orch->>ExtDetector: Check External<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>mTLS
    ExtDetector-->>Orch: Detection Result
    Detectors-->>Orch: Detection Result
    Orch->>LLMInf: Forward to LLM<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>mTLS
    LLMInf-->>Orch: LLM Response
    Orch-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>LLMApp: Final Response
